Hi,

In Portfolio for JIRA I can set estimates for each stage separatly. But when developer logs work in Jira, it reduces overall estimates for issue. Estimates for stages recalculated automaticaly depending on persantage.

It would be much better if developer could add type of work when he logs work. And estimates for concrete stage of work should be reduced in Portfolio.

h2. Description

Because of a bug in the topological sorting of issues in the schedule calculation you might experience unstable solutions (the schedule looks differently after recalculation without any changes in the plan) or an exception popping up from Portfolio with the following stacktrace:

