h2. Workaround

Unfortunately there is currently no known workaround for classic plans.
 If you are working with LivePlans the only known workaround is to temporarily disable dependency scheduling until the bug is fixed. 
 To do so click on the dots next to the plan name in Portfolio and hit Configure. In the section "Scheduling" set the option "Dependency Scheduling" to Off.

